+MSG = """CONVERSATION-HEALTH-GATE-A1 已 ACCEPTED (R4 verdict)。
+
+当前项目状态：
+- A1 完成：四层对话健康防御 (Pre-Task Hard Gate + Pre-GPT Gate 基础 + Evidence Pack + Pre-Commit Advisory 基础)
